import React from 'react';
import styled from 'styled-components';

const LogoContainer = styled.div`
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: ${props => props.theme.spacing.sm};
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: ${props => props.theme.transitions.base};
  
  &:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
`;

const LogoIcon = styled.div`
  width: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  height: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
`;

const LogoText = styled.span`
  font-family: ${props => props.theme.fonts.primary};
  font-weight: ${props => props.theme.fontWeights.bold};
  font-size: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? props.theme.fontSizes['2xl'] : 
                        props.size === 'medium' ? props.theme.fontSizes.xl : 
                        props.theme.fontSizes.lg};
  background: ${props => props.theme.colors.gradientPrimary};
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
`;

const LokanexLogo = ({ size = 'medium', showText = true, ...props }) => {
  return (
    <LogoContainer {...props}>
      <LogoIcon size={size}>
        <svg
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          viewBox="0 0 100 100"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          {/* Bottom-left cube - moved down and left */}
          <rect
            x="10"
            y="60"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            fill="url(#gradient1)"
            stroke="url(#strokeGradient)"
            strokeWidth="0.5"
            rx="3"
          />
          
          {/* Bottom-right cube - touching bottom-left */}
          <rect
            x="30"
            y="60"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            fill="url(#gradient1)"
            stroke="url(#strokeGradient)"
            strokeWidth="0.5"
            rx="3"
          />
          
          {/* Top-left cube - touching bottom-left */}
          <rect
            x="10"
            y="40"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            fill="url(#gradient1)"
            stroke="url(#strokeGradient)"
            strokeWidth="0.5"
            rx="3"
          />
          
          {/* Top-right cube - brought closer with enhanced styling */}
          <rect
            x="40"
            y="30"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            fill="url(#gradient4)"
            stroke="url(#accentStroke)"
            strokeWidth="0.8"
            rx="3"
          />
          
          {/* Subtle connecting line between L and orange cube */}
          <line
            x1="30"
            y1="50"
            x2="40"
            y2="40"
            stroke="url(#lineGradient)"
            strokeWidth="1.5"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            opacity="0.6"
          />
          
          {/* Subtle shadow/glow effect */}
          <rect
            x="40"
            y="30"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            fill="url(#glowGradient)"
            rx="3"
            opacity="0.3"
          />
          
          {/* Gradients */}
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="gradient1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="gradient2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="gradient3" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="gradient4" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="strokeGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ffffff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#e0e0e0" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="accentStroke" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ffffff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ffaa00" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="lineGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
            </linearGradient>
            <radialGradient id="glowGradient" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" stopOpacity="0.4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" stopOpacity="0.1" />
            </radialGradient>
          </defs>
        </svg>
      </LogoIcon>
      {showText && <LogoText size={size}>Lokanex</LogoText>}
    </LogoContainer>
  );
};

export default LokanexLogo;
